Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.46,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胆小爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:17.00,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}又想吻你的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:21.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比起去爱 比起去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:28.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却总是犹犹豫豫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}常常后悔着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心痛呢
